# Cursor rules ŌĆö Bonyad web app (Next.js 15 App Router)

You are working in the Bonyad Next.js 15 web app at the repo root. The architecture is fixed and binding. Full rules are in `CLAUDE.md` and `docs/`. Read them before writing code.

The folder `website-bonyad/` is the frozen legacy React Native codebase. It is `.gitignore`'d and read-only ŌĆö use it only to learn backend endpoints, auth flow, and request/response shapes. **Never copy UI, JSX, components, styling, or design from it.** Designs come from Figma.

## Tech stack (locked)

Next.js 15 App Router ┬Ę React 19 ┬Ę TypeScript strict ┬Ę Tailwind v4 with CSS-variable tokens ┬Ę shadcn/ui ┬Ę TanStack Query v5 ┬Ę Zustand v5 ┬Ę react-hook-form + zod ┬Ę i18next (init once) ┬Ę next-themes ┬Ę Vitest + RTL + Playwright + MSW.

## Hard rules (these are violated most often ŌĆö memorize)

1. **No `fetch()` outside `src/lib/api-client.ts`.** Always go through a TanStack Query hook in `features/X/api/`.
2. **No endpoint string literal outside `src/config/endpoints.ts`.** Mirror endpoints from `website-bonyad/src/config/api.ts` (the legacy RN app ŌĆö backend-integration reference only).
3. **No hardcoded colors, hex, RGB, or font-family.** Use Tailwind utilities backed by tokens in `src/styles/tokens.css`.
4. **No physical Tailwind direction utilities** (`ml-*`, `mr-*`, `pl-*`, `pr-*`, `left-*`, `right-*`, `text-left`, `text-right`). Use logical (`ms-*`, `me-*`, `ps-*`, `pe-*`, `start-*`, `end-*`, `text-start`, `text-end`) ŌĆö Arabic users need clean RTL.
5. **No user-facing string in JSX.** Always `t('namespace.key')` from `react-i18next`, with entries in both `locales/en.json` and `locales/ar.json`.
6. **Features cannot import from other features.** Lift shared code to `src/components/`, `src/hooks/`, `src/utils/`, etc.
7. **No `react-native`, `react-native-web`, `expo-*`, or `nativewind`** anywhere. The legacy app at `website-bonyad/src/` is **backend-integration reference only ŌĆö never copy UI, JSX, styling, or design.**
8. **File Ōēż 200 lines, function Ōēż 50 lines, complexity Ōēż 10, nesting Ōēż 4.** ESLint-enforced. If you hit a limit, extract.
9. **Server Component by default.** Add `'use client'` only at the leaf component that needs hooks/state/events.
10. **Every public page needs SSR + metadata + JSON-LD.** See `docs/seo-and-ai-readability.md`.
11. **JSON-LD must be HTML-escaped before `dangerouslySetInnerHTML`** and carry the CSP nonce. Use the `<JsonLd>` helper.
12. **No `process.env.X` outside `src/config/env.ts`.** All env access goes through the zod-validated `env` export.
13. **WCAG 2.2 AA target.** No `outline: none`, every icon-only button has `aria-label`, every form input has a real `<label>`.
14. **The legacy RN app is backend-integration reference ONLY.** Never copy UI/JSX/styling from it. Visuals come from Figma.
15. **No invented icons.** Every icon is an SVG exported from Figma, in `src/components/icons/`, with `currentColor` fills/strokes. `lucide-react` only for system glyphs whose default form matches the design.
16. **Every non-trivial task is split into phases with verification gates.** Phase 0 = plan and stop. After each phase, run typecheck/lint/test and wait for the user before continuing. See `docs/task-workflow.md`.

